Count Three relates to multiple alleged victims and the time period 1994 to 2004. Count Four of the indictment charges the defendant with transporting an individual under the age of 17 in interstate commerce, with the intent that the individual engage in sexual activity for which a person could be charged with a criminal offense. Count Six relates solely to Carolyn and the time period 2001 to 2004. Instruction No. 11. Multiple counts. As I just explained, the indictment contains six counts.
